lead_paragraph: World number one Novak Djokovic continued his dominance of Kei Nishikori with a 6-3 7-5 victory in the final of the Rogers Cup in Toronto on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Djokovic Beats Nishikori in Rogers Cup Final
